No. 1588,

October Term, 1970.

Sears, Roebuck & Co. et al. v. Solien, Regional Director, Natural Labor Relations Board, et al.,

403 U. S. 905, 404 U. S. 960. Motion for leave to file second petition for rehearing denied.

Mr. Justice Powell took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
